message:
Add `wfp-ui-guide` under `docs` dir

- Adds `grunt-jekyll` package, to help manage Jekyll builds;
- Adds new Grunt tasks for compiling UI docs.

Refs #14

Fix ESLint Grunt task

Replaced `grunt-eslint` with a much more versatile `eslint-grunt` package, enabling `--force` for ESLint, which will ensure only actual errors are shown.

This was preventing Travis CI from successfully finishing build tasks.

Ref #27
Add `grunticon` package, and ref it in Gruntfile

Install `node-style-guide` eslint config via NPM

Install [eslint-config-node-style-guide](https://www.npmjs.com/package/eslint-config-node-style-guide)

Ref #27
Update npm dependencies for the project

Update `eslint` configuration

- [x] Ignore linting for external libs, under `js/lib` path

Update `grunt` version dependency

Downgrade `grunt` from `^1.0.1` to `~0.4.5`.

Simplify npm dependency details

All dependencies are required, and theres no distinction between `devDependencies` and `dependencies`, so all of them have been unified under `dependencies`.

Add and configure copying resources between dirs

Refs #109

Initial commit of the next WFP UI, fork from https://github.com/carbon-design-system/carbon-components-react, logos, favicons and colors added, Sketch Component Library updated to the new UI, test framework for redux forms, documentation, Usabilla feedback, Components: Footer, Breadcrump, RfTextInput, Wrapper and some Carbon Design System Components
Documentation, Blockquote, Checkbox, User, Wrapper, BannerNavigation added, MainNavigation added, maybe switch to Hover states, Logo documentation
Right to left support added, colors are now variables
Readme and publish work in progress
Select Icon as after element to simplify use without framework
Snapshot testing added, TablePagination updated, Storybook Documentation Title highlighted
ModuleFooter added to Module, Storybook Documentation styling work in progress
ModulHeader has an optional right sided Option block now (like Facebook)
Icons added, App Icons added, Footer external added, Unit updated, List added
Naming and eslint documentation, Logo Documentation updated, Acronym added, WFP Icons updated
create-react-app and html sample application added
Input onChange trigger fix, IE11 compatibility for svg icons added
Grid documentation, css minification and autoprefixer build, Icon documentation updated
User component image default avatar check removed, MainNavigation children can now be null
css postcss updated, Select updated, external Redux form wrapper WiP
Alignment with Carbon Components WiP, getting the tests right, default centering for individual components

Footer Sample content updated, Tabs have an customTabContent option, TextArea bug fix, feature flags from carbon components added, autoswitching tabs on selecting right-top-left components and html only components
Credits updated, female and male icon added (very similar to the ones from FontAwesome)
Modal renders in Portal by default now (prop inPortal), FileUploader
Create-React-App example updated to v2, .env vars added
moved assets, classnames are now a dependency
Documentation updated, Story margins are now related to their siblings
Sample for react-select and custom styling wip, Tag Documentation, SubNavigation improved Documentation
StepNavigation and WizardForm wip, commit hook checks, react-select custom style and ReduxFormWrapper connector
Card Documentation and added multiple kinds, Wizard wip

resolved #161, Favicons link updated, FileUploader spacing smaller (request), vertical Radio Buttons, Step Navigation Items for skiped, warning and complete added to Documentation, Readme added to show Info
Modal update, Unit Story updated, Jest testing
fix(FileUploader): Typo in onFilesChanged, WFP Icons updated
fix(ReduxFormWrapper): children prop is now used instead of InputComponent (#173)
fix(User): tests fixed (#169), doc(Documentation): design updated, code highlighting, text updates
feat(Datepicker): added DatePicker and DateRangePicker draft using Airbnbs react-select (#175)
feat(Select): example for react-final-form added clean console.log from builds
feat(Slider): OnChange now returns int instead of object
feat(Icons): Upgrade to newer version, console.logs removed
refactor(esLint): cleanup for all warnings, pre-commit hook for console.log
refactor(Test): no commit without working tests
docs(readme): documentation now inline and better readme automatically loaded
docs(Favicons): favicons Generator added and documentation improved (#186)
docs(Icons): Icons documentation, Favicon, Storybook update
fix(NumberInput): controls work with Final Forms
feat(Notifications): added and Module patterns, etc.

feat(multiple): color nuances #189 and overall color page improvement, redirect page example in handlebars added, Blockquote update, Android UI docs Wip, DatePicker, List has new styles (simple-inline, list-colon), Select Carbon Components update, Dashboard documentation
docs(Filter): filter demo added and documentation, Unit propTypes and docs
fix(Tests): fixing tests and removing dublicated test
docs(readme): updates and dynamic props added
feat(multiple): added code examples, accessibility tests, story source
feat(NumberInput): empty values are now possible
feat(Tooltip): added new tippy react implementation (#205)
feat(Tooltip): moving to new Tippy package
feat(Colours): support colours added and documentation updated
feat(Tabs): resize observer to calculate underline position #210
feat(Storybook): favicon now visible in build
feat(icons): custom colors are now supported, emergency icons added
feat(colours): new colour page and changelog
docs(Colour): automated colour contrast checker added
docs(Storybook): upgrading storybook and added docs for maps
feat(Tabs): resize detector removed and replaced with own solution, tests fixed
feat(Storybook): sorting feature, upgrade Storybook add SDG logo to icons
feat(NumberInput): new number input using hooks
feat(Dependencies): update all dependencies to the latest version
fix(css): removed css modules and use with regular scss to increase customizability
fix(package): using rollup for smaller and faster package
docs(Components): added documentation to serval components
feat(Multiple): react-dropzone added, InputGroup docs, Table docs, Tooltip wip, Tabs without animation
docs(Favicon): added favicon and updated build process
docs(Favicon): pipeline and build process fix
docs(Favicon): moving favion generation into build-storybook
docs(Components): port documentations from old to new environment
fix(Multiple): formGroup improvements, and multiple other changes

  docs(components): footer fixes and typography documentation in progress
